    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "={{ $json.markdown }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are The Teacher AI agent.\n\nYour task is to transform the provided content into a study-ready learning summary for a student preparing for a quiz or exam.\n\nThe student must be able to:\n- understand the topic\n- remember key facts\n- answer quiz questions correctly\n\nGenerate:\n- summary\n- difficulty (one of: beginner, basic, intermediate, advanced, expert)\n- title extracted or inferred from the content for material saving\n\nRules:\n- summary must contain 5–7 items  + main concepts\n- each item MUST start with a number and dot (e.g. \"1. \")\n- each item must be a short clear sentence\n- Each point MUST be on a new line.\n- Do NOT put all points in one line.\n- no extra text\n\nDo NOT return JSON Schema.\n\nWrong:\n\n{\n  \"type\":\"object\",\n  \"properties\":{...}\n}\n\nCorrect:\n\n{\n  \"summary\":\"value\",\n  \"difficulty\":\"value\",\n  \"title\":\"value\"\n}\n"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        -384,
        16
      ],
      "id": "6d6655fe-9e91-4697-be73-99f2441ff654",
      "name": "AI Teacher Agent",
      "onError": "continueErrorOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "={{ $json.summary }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are The Examiner AI agent.\n\nYour task is to generate exactly 5 multiple-choice quiz questions based on the provided study summary.\n\nEach question must be independent and suitable for storing as a database row.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\nFormat:\n\n{\n  \"rows\": [\n    {\n      \"question_id\": \"string\",\n      \"question\": \"string\",\n      \"options\": \"string (multiline)\",\n      \"correct\": \"A, B, C or D\",\n      \"explanation\": \"string\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nRules:\n- exactly 5 rows\n- questions must be based strictly on the provided summary\n- options must be a SINGLE STRING formatted for Telegram\n- each option must be on a new line\n- each option must follow this format:\n  A) text\n  B) text\n  C) text\n  D) text\n- correct must be one of: A, B, C, or D\n- do not favor option A\n- randomize correct answer position for each question\n- only one correct answer per question\n- explanation as a short sentence (can be based on summary)\n- question_id one of 1, 2, 3, 4, or 5 reflecting question order\n- no markdown\n- no extra text"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
